==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Percolation
<hw>Per`co*la"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>percolatio</ets>.]</ety> <def>The act or process of percolating, or
filtering; filtration; straining. Specifically <fld>(Pharm.)</fld>, the
process of exhausting the virtues of a powdered drug by letting a liquid
filter slowly through it.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Percolator</ent>⟦br⟧
